content:
More developed version of 0.2, however still a leak and not intended for release.
It removed some warp pipes in the Castle Grounds and removed lots of unused areas.

New Areas:
Course 2 Area 4: Plexal Basement (warped)
Course 5 Area 3: Mountain (b-roll, inaccessible)
Course 7 Area 3: Sky Stronghold
OW-1 Area 4: Beta Lobby A
Metal Cap Area 1: Mountain (b-roll)
